iTunes Sync
Drew Stephens <drew@dinomite.net>

Sync an iTunes library—music and all—from one Mac to another.  I use this to
pull all of my music from my desktop to my laptop.

Usage:
    itunes_sync.pl [options] user remote_host

Options:
    -help
        This help message

    -remote
        Remote iTunes directory (default: /Users/<user>/Music/iTunes)

    -local
        Local iTunes directory (default: /Users/<user>/Music/iTunes)

    -bwlimit
        Bandwidth limit

    -nolibrary
        Don't copy the iTunes library file

